{"tid":84312,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"渣打信用卡繳費問題","createTime":"2017-01-17T12:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T06:25:54.000Z","uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bcda3d94b906b1e4236c46afc1cc1c0e03093f2a","tid":84312,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:26:57.000Z","msg":"話說我預先入左6000蚊落張信用額10000既卡度，<br />\n就諗住交一筆16000蚊既帳單，<br />\n諗住交完之後就做分期，但係佢淨係比我交1萬蚊不突止，<br />\n交完先知係計現金透支<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無得做分期<br />\n問題就黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我仲有6千蚊credit limit係張卡度，我應該找4000蚊卡數 定係找足1萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncard centre 果個職員又答唔實我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係話以月結單為準<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲有經驗可以話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為如果係找足一萬蚊我找唔到住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dbc73f097ec8ea50e01db611515278e1316c6fb","tid":84312,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9236fb99261b0e87f444a198f84f6b4c7cba8ed1","tid":84312,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c7a8df05d1d76a9d2362952b265cf8e27890eb","tid":84312,"uid":9467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"咁真係以月結單為主 睇statement 先啦"},{"pid":"ba2df4bd32805b47edeb01b34e97b9dd0c58d505","tid":84312,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:10:57.000Z","msg":"交學費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0319ab9f8f6a6e4d63ef5b50a5ff6b513b44bea1","tid":84312,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁真係以月結單為主 睇statement 先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 銀行無明確既計算方式既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ea63d83419971da80b986df0121d74d0234ed0","tid":84312,"uid":41928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁真係以月結單為主 睇statement 先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 銀行無明確既計算方式既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落分行問，Card Centre廢的。理論上，一開始透支左10000，然後還6000，應該尚有4000limit用。如果佢當你用左10000limit，咁剩底個6000去左邊？銀行唔可以無緣無故扣住你d錢，你可以向金管局投訴，同時入稟小額錢債審裁處，追收個筆錢衍生的幾仙利息，叫渣打個主席出庭答辯。呢個時候到你做阿爺。<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹鳩up。"},{"pid":"8ef4411c617bc227e637f21ca194186dd371869b","tid":84312,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:07:00.000Z","msg":"你即日做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55577945e0b6dab90723e004cf4aae17448d269","tid":84312,"uid":41928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁真係以月結單為主 睇statement 先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 銀行無明確既計算方式既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落分行問，Card Centre廢的。理論上，一開始透支左10000，然後還6000，應該尚有4000limit用。如果佢當你用左10000limit，咁剩底個6000去左邊？銀行唔可以無緣無故扣住你d錢，你可以向金管局投訴，同時入稟小額錢債審裁處，追收個筆錢衍生的幾仙利息，叫渣打個主席出庭答辯。呢個時候到你做阿爺。<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹鳩up。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落分行問，Card Centre廢的。理論上，一開始透支左10000，然後還6000，應該尚有6000limit用。如果佢當你用左10000limit，咁剩底個6000去左邊？銀行唔可以無緣無故扣住你d錢，你可以向金管局投訴，同時入稟小額錢債審裁處，追收個筆錢衍生的幾仙利息，叫渣打個主席出庭答辯。呢個時候到你做阿爺。<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹鳩up。"},{"pid":"860ca1dd443c2955e9aa9c29f4d2101c1ec29f1c","tid":84312,"uid":31437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"你個時間線係點既先"},{"pid":"f000e45ac3538db1341abe6bb7b038f094ed5f79","tid":84312,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T20:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主柒撚懵懵"},{"pid":"f636b3d735d3ecff4e7b0767c0cf750ad0403958","tid":84312,"uid":21455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T20:21:25.000Z","msg":"如果自己入到錢就加大到個credit limit,咁個credit limit仲有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b817d7871c7d6c355bf6e47c2a0df20fa8ec3e","tid":84312,"uid":32396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T20:25:37.000Z","msg":"照計你剩係交左1萬 你原本入左6000<br />\n應該係還4000 如果還10000咁你果6000蚊去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  照道理就應該咁計"},{"pid":"9df2c5919eeee4a5bd2289733282d30b706177bf","tid":84312,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T20:51:47.000Z","msg":"你係咪入完6000之後即刻就交16000單先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b203f299b4206e829fc0fbe3c1833cb5f116a2e","tid":84312,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T20:53:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果自己入到錢就加大到個credit limit,咁個credit limit仲有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係d學生卡得1皮limit 點交學費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個limit 只係銀行每個月最多肯借幾多錢俾你"},{"pid":"94ca53af91720c2b545a890898c00d627216b83d","tid":84312,"uid":21455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:46:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果自己入到錢就加大到個credit limit,咁個credit limit仲有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係d學生卡得1皮limit 點交學費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個limit 只係銀行每個月最多肯借幾多錢俾你</blockquote><br />\n咁樓主情況應該係佢即日入錢即日交所以先咁？"},{"pid":"5f28c3c34c7f8bc45e0b4eb93499a776a9fbfccf","tid":84312,"uid":10279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"如果咁緊係入完等幾日先 點會即刻交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1277c935bfb6aac59eb979defe7a5e9382428d78","tid":84312,"uid":3264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:44:57.000Z","msg":"有ebanking就上網check下<br />\n正常都要等一日先交啦"},{"pid":"c025003a9d54502cf3bc33090081e7ba7c89a39e","tid":84312,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果自己入到錢就加大到個credit limit,咁個credit limit仲有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係d學生卡得1皮limit 點交學費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個limit 只係銀行每個月最多肯借幾多錢俾你</blockquote><br />\n咁樓主情況應該係佢即日入錢即日交所以先咁？</blockquote><br />\n應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEbanking 入錢落信用卡通常都要幾個工作天先入到條數落到去"},{"pid":"9b3050511529ab6731f3a86e11c69ac37d1c063e","tid":84312,"uid":15916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"等月結單出先好找數 唔好亂找<br />\n如果唔係你唔知自己比左未"},{"pid":"39d666ffef52c2eaabdd11ff4f365d9a3937439f","tid":84312,"uid":30680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:16:29.000Z","msg":"渣打星期1-5 ATM每晚10點截一次數 截數前入第二日9點先用到個credit<br />\nweekend 入就唔清楚 樓主好大機會係張卡未回到氣就去左比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef41e669532b24dfd674a6e0fc775f1522decdcc","tid":84312,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:31:41.000Z","msg":"你要睇下係咪真係入落卡果個AC. <br />\n我情況係一個INTERGRATE AC, 同2個CREDIT卡戶口.<br />\n咁我就同時開左1張提款卡同2張信用卡, <br />\n但入錢一定要過去信用卡先找到數. <br />\n雖然我網上睇可以同時睇晒3個戶口.<br />\n亦可以用提款卡網上找信用卡數.<br />\n但你唔轉過去唔識自己轉數過去找.<br />\n<br />\n你CHECK一CHECK. 我試過咁情況"},{"pid":"3b0043e64de3ceb131e469faa3e0145126d3a355","tid":84312,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:53:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要睇下係咪真係入落卡果個AC. <br />\n我情況係一個INTERGRATE AC, 同2個CREDIT卡戶口.<br />\n咁我就同時開左1張提款卡同2張信用卡, <br />\n但入錢一定要過去信用卡先找到數. <br />\n雖然我網上睇可以同時睇晒3個戶口.<br />\n亦可以用提款卡網上找信用卡數.<br />\n但你唔轉過去唔識自己轉數過去找.<br />\n<br />\n你CHECK一CHECK. 我試過咁情況</blockquote><br />\n咁梗係啦，你入錢去saving account無啦啦點會幫你自動找數"},{"pid":"c44c1734efbec241dce1292a5d5a5bf597635b02","tid":84312,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:58:19.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位巴絲關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係我16號入，17號交<br />\n但我諗張卡限左每日個現金透支額係每日一萬<br />\n去到第二日預先入定果6千已經變左即刻找左條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我諗我找埋淨低果4千就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過就蝕左個手續費比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外我想點樣用張信用卡套現最化算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未出糧但比依壇野搞到亂左啲budget<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06454aee91893211f7456b744269d27222bec0c","tid":84312,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝咁多位巴絲關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係我16號入，17號交<br />\n但我諗張卡限左每日個現金透支額係每日一萬<br />\n去到第二日預先入定果6千已經變左即刻找左條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我諗我找埋淨低果4千就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過就蝕左個手續費比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外<span style=\"color: red;\">我想問</span>點樣用張信用卡套現最化算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未出糧但比依壇野搞到亂左啲budget<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}